THIS README VALID AS ON 20.06.2015

Download cgminer version 3.7.2 built from this page : "https://litecointalk.org/index.php?topic=10030.0"

- extract the folder from the downloaded archive, cd into it:
- copy the 2 .sh files (first-time-setup.sh and mine-litecoins.sh) into this extracted folder

FOR THE FIRST TIME DO THIS:
sudo ln -s /usr/lib/libncurses.so.5 /usr/lib/libtinfo.so.5
sudo ln -s /usr/lib/libtinfo.so.5 /usr/lib/libtinfo.so

AND also install libcurl-compat from aur:
yaourt -S lincurl-compat
(this first time stup in first-time-setup.sh)

then run the mine-litecoins.sh script.